articles.title: About Robert W. Walker, Ph. D.
articles.description: More about the author and this website
articles.contents:
Robert W. Walker is Associate Professor of Quantitative Methods in the Atkinson Graduate School of Management of Willamette University where I teach courses in data science and statistics.
This is an example template for a Distill website.
